 Oasis 分享《Definitely Maybe》30 周年再版中的《Columbia (Sawmills Outtake)》 https://www.nme.com/news/music/oasis-share-columbia-sawmills-outtake-from-definitely-maybe-30th-anniversary-reissue-3765199?utm_source=rss&utm_medium=rss&utm_campaign=oasis-share-columbia-锯木厂 - 绝对可能 - 30 周年纪念重新发行Tom SkinnerThu, 13 Jun 2024 08:01:18 +0000 Music NewsNewsBritpopIndie https://www.nme.com/?p=3765199 <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/OasisDefinitelyMaybe-30th-anniversary-reissue.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="Oasis 的 Noel 和 Liam Gallagher 的黑白照片" decoding="async" fetchpriority="high" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/OasisDefinitelyMaybe-30th-anniversary-reissue.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/OasisDefinitelyMaybe-30th-anniversary-reissue-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/OasisDefinitelyMaybe-30th-anniversary-reissue-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/OasisDefinitelyMaybe-30th-anniversary-reissue-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/OasisDefinitelyMaybe-30th-anniversary-reissue-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/OasisDefinitelyMaybe-30th-anniversary-reissue-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p>该歌曲的“催眠”扩展版本标志着即将推出的专辑的首次预览</p><p><a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/oasis-share-columbia-sawmills-outtake-from-definitely-maybe-30th-anniversary-reissue-3765199">Oasis 分享的《Definitely Maybe》30 周年纪念再版中的《Columbia (Sawmills Outtake)》</a>首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ; <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/OasisDefinitelyMaybe-30th-anniversary-reissue.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="Oasis 的 Noel 和 Liam Gallagher 的黑白照片" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/OasisDefinitelyMaybe-30th-anniversary-reissue.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/OasisDefinitelyMaybe-30th-anniversary-reissue-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/OasisDefinitelyMaybe-30th-anniversary-reissue-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/OasisDefinitelyMaybe-30th-anniversary-reissue-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/OasisDefinitelyMaybe-30th-anniversary-reissue-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/OasisDefinitelyMaybe-30th-anniversary-reissue-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/oasis">Oasis</a>分享了他们即将推出的<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/oasis-announce-30th-anniversary-reissue-of-definitely-maybe-featuring-unheard-versions-3758723">30 周年纪念版“Definitely Maybe”</a>中前所未闻的“Columbia”版本。下面听听。</p><p>这支英伦流行乐队上个月宣布，他们 1994 年经典首张专辑的特别重新发行版将于 8 月 30 日通过 Big Brother Recordings 发行（<a href="https://oasismusic.lnk.to/DM30" target="_blank" rel="noopener">在此处预订</a>）。</p><ul class="post-content-read-more"><li><strong>阅读更多： <a href="https://www.nme.com/features/music-interviews/noel-gallagher-interview-oasis-council-skies-3451058">诺埃尔·加拉格尔（Noel Gallagher）：“世界是一个美丽的地方——只是居住着混蛋”</a></strong></li></ul><p>它有多种格式可供选择，其中包含 Monnow Valley Studios 废弃的原始录音室的录音，以及康沃尔郡 Sawmills Studios 的最终专辑录音室的片段。</p><p>今天（6 月 13 日），该系列的首个预览以“Columbia (Sawmills Outtake)”的形式发布，这是由<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/noel-gallagher">Noel Gallagher</a>和 Callum Marinho 首次混音的。</p><p>这首歌的早期扩展版本长达七分钟多，并且基于有效简单的和弦结构。它拥有“催眠节奏”，“盘旋成延迟的鼓声和嗡嗡声的反馈”。</p><p>诺埃尔的和声在混音中比欧文·莫里斯的最终专辑版本埋得更深。该曲目附有新的官方歌词视频 - 您可以在此处收听： </p><p><iframe title="绿洲 - 哥伦比亚 (Sawmills Outtake) [官方歌词视频]" width="696" height="392" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/QVjjrOZDKNo?feature=oembed" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" referrerpolicy="strict-origin-when-cross-origin" allowfullscreen></iframe></p><p> 《Columbia》是 Oasis 最早创作的歌曲之一，最初以白标 12 英寸黑胶唱片形式发行。</p><p> 《Definitely Maybe》的 30 周年纪念再版还包括由<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/liam-gallagher">Liam Gallagher</a>演唱的《Sad Song》未发行的演示版。</p><p>描述中写道：“蒙诺谷的录音和锯木厂的录音现在首次出土，为最终完成的文章的过程提供了新的、令人信服的理解。</p><p> “凭借其原始的边缘和不安的能量，《Definitely Maybe》听起来总是像是一张已经完全成型的专辑——然而，新发布的版本为歌迷提供了对这张专辑的迷人的新见解；展示了早年推动 Oasis 发展的自信以及首次亮相所需的决心。”</p><p>它补充道：“直到现在，重新审视 30 年前的档案，表明了录音过程在讲述有史以来最重要的专辑之一的艰难创作故事方面的重要性。” </p><p><iframe title="利亚姆·加拉格尔 (Liam Gallagher) 于格拉斯顿伯里和纳内沃斯 (Glastonbury &amp; Knebworth) 的石玫瑰 (The Stone Roses) 演出第一" width="696" height="392" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/j27A15yBBE8?feature=oembed" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" referrerpolicy="strict-origin-when-cross-origin" allowfullscreen></iframe></p><p> &#39;Columbia (Sawmills Outtake)&#39; 的到来正值 Liam <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/watch-liam-gallaghers-official-footage-of-kicking-off-definitely-maybe-anniversary-tour-in-sheffield-3761988">在英国和爱尔兰继续他的 &#39;Definitely Maybe&#39; 30 周年纪念巡演</a>之际。</p><p> LG 在演出中完整播放了这张唱片，并播放了那个时代的许多其他曲目，包括<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/noel-gallagher">诺埃尔</a>演唱的“Half The World Away”（ <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/liam-gallagher-says-noel-is-still-playing-hard-to-get-at-definitely-maybe-show-3762205">他献给他疏远的兄弟和前乐队成员</a>）和<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/watch-the-moment-liam-gallagher-covered-noels-oasis-era-lock-all-the-doors-on-definitely-maybe-30th-anniversary-tour-3761773">诺埃尔绿洲时代的“Lock All” The Doors 的演示</a>。</p><p>您可以在下面查看即将到来的日期的完整列表，并<a href="https://www.ticketmaster.co.uk/liam-gallagher-tickets/artist/2055477?irgwc=1&amp;utm_source=2862475-NME%20Networks%20Media%20Limited&amp;utm_medium=affiliate&amp;utm_campaign=2862475&amp;awtrc=&amp;clickId=wwEzBLW-RxyPWNIXqSXj8x-BUkHVRdRecSNiXA0&amp;camefrom=CFC_BUYAT_2862475&amp;ircid=7559" target="_blank" rel="noopener">在此处查找任何剩余的门票</a>。</p><p> <str